<div class="container">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">

      <h3>Programme</h3>
      <p>As TTC is a contest and not a workshop or conference, it has a rather unusual format. The morning of the contest will be used to score the solutions to the offline cases (FIXML and Movie Database). The afternoon of the contest will be used to score solutions to the live contest (a transformation problem that will be announced on Monday 21st July). The purpose of the morning and afternoon sessions is the same: to present your solution, score the solutions of others, and to crown an overall winner in each category.</p>

      <!-- <h4>Monday 20th July</h4>
      <p>1400 - 1405 : The live contest will be announced in <strong>PX001</strong>, and the supporting resources (metamodels, models, testcases, etc.) will be made available.</p>

      <h4>Tuesday 21st July</h4>
      <p>0900 - 0905 : The live contest announcement will be repeated in <strong>PX001</strong>. -->

      <h4>Monday 20th July, Tuesday 21st July, Wednesday 22nd July, Thursday 23rd July</h4>
      <p>All day - Hackspace will be available (location TBC) for you to work on your solutions to the live contest, or to talk about transformations with other contestants and TTC organisers.</p>

      <h4>Friday 24th July</h4>
      <p>The morning sessions is dedicated to the offline cases (FIXML and Movie Database) and has two parallel tracks:</p>

      <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Time</th>
            <th>FIXML Track (PT/006)</th>
            <th>Movie Database Track (PT/007)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <strong>8.45</strong>
            </td>
            <td colspan="2">
              <strong><a href="/presentations/welcome.pdf">Welcome</a> (PT/006)</strong>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <% data.schedule_morning.each do |slot| %>
            <%
              fixml_solution = slot.fixml? ? data.solutions_fixml[slot.fixml] : nil
              movie_solution = slot.movie? ? data.solutions_movie[slot.movie] : nil
            %>
            <tr>
              <td><strong><%=slot.time%></strong></td>
              <td>
                <% if fixml_solution %>
                  <strong><%=fixml_solution.tool%> - <%=fixml_solution.authors%></strong><br/>
                  <em>
                    <%=data.solutions_fixml[(slot.fixml - 2) % data.solutions_fixml.length].authors%><br/>
                    <%=data.solutions_fixml[(slot.fixml - 1) % data.solutions_fixml.length].authors%>
                  </em><br/><br/>
                  <a href="/solutions/fixml/ttc2014_submission_<%=fixml_solution.pdf%>.pdf">PDF Description</a> |
                  <% if fixml_solution.share.empty? %>
                    <strong>No SHARE demo</strong>
                  <% else %>
                    <a href="<%=fixml_solution.share%>">SHARE Demo</a>
                  <% end %>
                <% end%>
              </td>
              <td>
                <% if movie_solution %>
                  <strong><%=movie_solution.tool%> - <%=movie_solution.authors%></strong><br/>
                  <em>
                    <%=data.solutions_movie[(slot.movie - 2) % data.solutions_movie.length].authors%><br/>
                    <%=data.solutions_movie[(slot.movie - 1) % data.solutions_movie.length].authors%>
                  </em><br/><br/>
                  <a href="/solutions/movie/ttc2014_submission_<%=movie_solution.pdf%>.pdf">PDF Description</a> |
                  <% if movie_solution.share.empty? %>
                    <strong>No SHARE demo</strong>
                  <% else %>
                    <a href="<%=movie_solution.share%>">SHARE Demo</a>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>

      <p>The afternoon session is dedicated to the live contest, and more details will be announced when the contestants are known.<p>

      <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Time</th>
            <th>Demo (Location PT/006)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <strong>14.00</strong>
            </td>
            <td>
              <strong>Welcome</strong>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <% data.schedule_afternoon.each do |slot| %>
            <tr>
              <td><strong><%=slot.time%></strong></td>
              <td>
                <% if slot.tool? %>
                  <strong><%=slot.tool%> - <%=slot.authors%></strong><br/>
                  <a href="/solutions/live/ttc2014_submission_<%=slot.pdf%>.pdf">PDF Description</a> |
                  <% if slot.share.empty? %>
                    <strong>No SHARE demo</strong>
                  <% else %>
                    <a href="<%=slot.share%>">SHARE Demo</a>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>

            <tr>
              <td>
                <strong>17.00</strong>
              </td>
              <td>
                <strong>Awards and <a href="/presentations/wrapup.pdf">Wrap Up</a></strong>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td>
                <strong>17.30</strong>
              </td>
              <td>
                <strong>Contest ends</strong>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

      </div>
  </div>
</div>
